quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  30,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  30,1,a l- meem
  30,2,Roomi qareeb ki sarzamen mein maghloob ho gay hain
  30,3,aur apni iss maghloobiat ke baad chand saal ke andar woh ghalib ho jayen ge
  30,4,Allah hi ka ikhtiyar hai pehlay bhi aur baad mein bhi aur woh din woh ho ga jabkay Allah ki bakhsh hui fatah par musalman khusihyan manayeen ge
  30,5,"Allah nusrat ataa farmata hai jisay chahta hai, aur woh zabardast aur Raheem hai"
  30,6,"yeh wada Allah ne kya hai, Allah kabhi apne waday ki khilaaf warzi nahi karta, magar aksar log nahi jantay hain"
  30,7,log duniya ki zindagi ka bas zahiri pehlu jantay hain aur akhirat se woh khud hi ghaafil hain
  30,8,kya unhon ne kabhi apne aap mein ghhor o fikar nahi kya? Allah ne zameen aur asmano ko aur unn saari cheezon ko jo unn ke darmain hain barhaq aur aik muqarrar muddat hi ke liye peda kya hai magar bohat se log apne rab ki mulaqaat ke munkir hain
  30,9,"aur kya yeh log kabhi zameen mein chalay phiray nahi hain ke aِnhin unn logon ka injaam nazar aata jo inn se pehlay guzar chuke hain? woh inn se ziyada taaqat rakhtay thay, onhon ne zameen ko khoob udehra tha aur ussay itna abad kya tha jitna unhon ne nahi kya hai unn ke paas un ke rasool roshan nishanain le kar aeye phir Allah un par zulm karne wala nah tha, magar woh khud hi apne oopar zulm kar rahay thay"
  30,10,"Aakhirkar jin logon ne buraiyan ki theen un ka injaam bohat bura howa, is liye ke unhon ne Allah ki ayaat ko jhatlaya tha aur woh un ka mazaq uratay thay"
  30,11,"Allah hi Khalq ki ibtida karta hai, phir wohi is ka iada kere ga, phir isi ki taraf tum pultayjao ge"
  30,12,aur jab woh saa-at barpaa ho gi is din mujrim hook dik reh jayen ge
  30,13,un ke tehra-ay hue sharikon mein koi un ka sfarshi nah ho ga aur woh apne sharikon ke munkir ho jayen ge
  30,14,"jis roz woh saa-at barpaa ho gi, is din ( sab ensaan ) allag garohoon mein Butt jayen ge"
  30,15,jo log imaan laaye hain aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye hain woh aik baagh mein Shadan o Ferhan rakhay jayen ge
  30,16,aur jinhon ne kufar kya hai aur hamari ayaat ko aur akhirat ki mulaqaat ko jhatlaya hai woh azaab mein haazir rakhay jayen ge
  30,17,pas tasbeeh karo Allah ki jabkay tum shaam karte ho aur jab subah karte ho
  30,18,asmano aur zameen mein usi ke liye hamd hai aur ( tasbeeh karo is ki ) teesray pehar aur jabkay tum par Zahar ka waqt aata hai
  30,19,woh zindah mein se murdy ko nikalta hai aur murdy mein se zindah ko nikalta hai aur zameen ko is ki mout ke baad zindagi bakhshta hai isi terhan tum log bhi ( haalat mout se ) nikaal liye jao ge
  30,20,uss ki nishanion mein se yeh hai ke is ne tum ko matti se peda kya phir yakayak tum bashar ho ke ( zameen mein ) phailtay chalay ja rahay ho
  30,21,aur is ki nishanion mein se yeh hai ke is ne tumahray liye tumhari hi jins se biwiyan banayen taakay tum un ke paas sukoon haasil karo aur tumahray darmain mohabbat aur rehmat peda kar di yaqeenan is mein bohat si nishanain hai unn logon ke liye jo ghhor o fikar karte hain
  30,22,"aur is ki nishanion mein se asmano aur zameen ki paidaiesh, aur tumhari zabanon aur tumahray rangon ka ikhtilaaf hai yaqeenan is mein bohat si nishanain hain danishmand logon ke liye"
  30,23,aur uss ki nishanion mein se tumhara raat aur din ko sona aur tumhara is ke fazl ko talaash karna hai yaqeenan iss mein bohat si nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ( ghhor se ) suntay hain
  30,24,"aur uss ki nishanion mein se yeh hai ke woh tumhe bijli ki chamak dekhata hai khauf ke sath bhi aur tama ke sath bhi aur aasman se pani barsata hai, phir is ke zareya se zameen ko is ki mout ke baad zindagi bakhshta hai yaqeenan iss mein bohat si nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letay hain"
  30,25,"aur uss ki nishanion mein se yeh hai ke aasman aur zameen is ke hukum se qaim hain phir jounhi ke uss ne tumhe zameen se puraka, bas aik hi pukaar mein achanak tum nikal aao ge"
  30,26,"asmano aur zameen mein jo bhi hain uss ke bande hain, sab ke sab isi ke tabay farmaan hain"
  30,27,"wohi hai jo takhleeq ki ibtida karta hai, phir wohi is ka iada kere ga aur yeh is ke liye aasaan tar hai asmano aur zameen mein is ki sift sab se bartar hai aur woh zabardast aur hakeem hai"
  30,28,woh tumhe khud tumhari apni hi zaat se aik misaal deta hai kya tumahray unn ghulamoo mein se jo tumhari malkiat mein hain kuch ghulam aisay bhi hain jo hamaray diye hue maal o doulat mein tumahray sath barabar ke shareek hon aur tum unn se uss terhan drtay ho jis terhan aapas mein apne peghambron se drtay ho? is terhan hum ayaat khol kar paish karte hain unn logon ke liye jo aqal se kaam letay hain
  30,29,magar yeh zalim be samjhay boojhay apne takhayulaat ke peechay chal parre hain ab kon uss shakhs ko rasta dikha sakta hai jisay Allah ne bhatka diya ho aisay logon ka to koi madad gaar nahi ho sakta
  30,30,"pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, aur NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ke پیروؤں ) yak soo ho kar apna rukh iss deen ki simt mein jama do, qaim ho jao uss fitrat par jis par Allah taala ne insanon ko peda kya hai, Allah ki banai hui saakht badli nahi ja sakti, yahi bilkul raast aur durust deen hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  30,31,"( qaim ho jao iss baat par ) Allah ki taraf rujoo karte hue, aur daro uss se, aur namaz qaim karo, aur nah ho jao unn mushriqeen mein se"
  30,32,"jinhon ne apna apna deen allag bana liya hai aur garohoon mein Butt gay hain, har aik giroh ke paas jo kuch hai isi mein woh magan hai"
  30,33,"logon ka haal yeh hai ke jab inhen koi takleef pahunchti hai to apne rab ki taraf rujoo kar ke ussay pukarte hain, phir jab woh kuch apni rehmat ka zayega inhen chakkha deta hai to yakayak un mein se kuch log shirk karne lagtay hain"
  30,34,"taakay hamaray kiye hue ahsaan ki nashukri karen acha, mazay kar lau, anqareeb tumhe maloom ho jaye ga"
  30,35,kya hum ne koi sanad aur Daleel un par nazil ki hai jo shahadat deti ho is shirk ki sadaqat par jo yeh kar rahay hain ?
  30,36,"jab hum logon ko rehmat ka zayega chukhatay hain to woh is par phool jatay hain, aur jab un ke apne kiye krtoton se un par koi museebat aati hai to yakayak woh mayoos honay lagtay hain"
  30,37,kya yeh log dekhte nahi hain ke Allah hi rizaq kushadah karta hai jis ka chahta hai aur tang karta hai ( jis ka chahta hai ) yaqeenan is mein bohat si nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo imaan laatay hain
  30,38,"pas ( ae momin ) rishta daar ko is ka haq day aur maskeen o musafir ko ( uss ka haq ) yeh tareeqa behtar hai unn logon ke liye jo Allah ki khushnodi chahtay hon, aur wohi Falah panay walay hain"
  30,39,"jo sood tum dete ho taakay logon ke amwal mein shaamil ho kar woh barh jaye, Allah ke nazdeek woh nahi barhta, aur jo zkoh tum Allah ki khushnodi haasil karne ke iraday se dete ho, isi ke dainay walay Dur haqeeqat apne maal berhate hain"
  30,40,"Allah hi hai jis ne tum ko peda kya, phir tumhe rizaq diya, phir woh tumhe mout deta hai, phir woh tumhe zindah kere ga kya tumahray tehra-ay hue sharikon mein koi aisa hai jo un mein se koi kaam bhi karta ho? pak hai woh aur bohat baala o bartar hai uss shirk se jo yeh log karte hain ?"
  30,41,"khushki aur tri mein fasaad barpaa ho gaya hai logon ke apne hathon ki kamaai se taakay maza chukha-ay unn ko un ke baaz aamaal ka, shayad ke woh baz ayen"
  30,42,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) inn se kaho ke zameen mein chal phir kar dekho pehlay guzray hue logon ka kya injaam ho chuka hai, un mein se aksar mushriq hi thay"
  30,43,pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) apna rukh mazbooti ke sath jama do iss deen raast ki simt mein qabal is ke ke woh din aeye jis ke tal jaane ki koi soorat Allah ki taraf se nahi hai uss din log phatt kar aik doosray se allag ho jayen ge
  30,44,jis ne kufar kya hai is ke kufar ka wabaal isi par hai aur jin logon ne naik amal kya hai woh apne hi liye Falah ka rasta saaf kar rahay hain
  30,45,taakay Allah imaan laane walon aur Amal Saleh karne walon ko apne fazl se jaza day yaqeenan woh kafiroon ko pasand nahi karta
  30,46,uss ki nishanion mein se yeh hai ke woh hawae bhejta hai basharat dainay ke liye aur tumhe apni rehmat se behra mand karne ke liye aur is gharz ke liye ke kashtiyan is ke hukum se chalein aur tum is ka fazl talaash karo aur is ke shukar guzaar bano
  30,47,"aur hum ne tum se pehlay Rasolo-n ko un ki qoum ki taraf bheja aur woh un ke paas roshan nishanain le kar aeye, phir jinhon ne jurm kya unn se hum ne intiqam liya aur hum par yeh haq tha ke hum mominon ki madad karen"
  30,48,"Allah hi hai jo hawaon ko bhejta hai aur woh baadal athati hain, phir woh inn baadalon ko aasman mein phela deta hai jis terhan chahta hai aur inhen tkrhyon mein taqseem karta hai, phir too daikhta hai ke barish ke qatray baadal se tpke chalay atay hain yeh barish jab woh apne bundon mein se jin par chahta hai barsata hai"
  30,49,to yakayak woh khush o Khurram ho jatay hain halaank is ke nuzool se pehlay woh mayoos ho rahay thay
  30,50,"dekho Allah ki rehmat ke asraat ke murda pari hui zameen ko woh kis terhan jِla uthata hai, yaqeenan woh mُrdon ko zindagi bakhsnay wala hai aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai"
  30,51,aur agar hum aik aisi howa bhaij den jis ke assar se woh apni khaiti ko zard payen to woh kufar karte reh jatay hain
  30,52,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) tum mُrdon ko nahi suna satke, nah unn behroon ko apni pukaar suna satke ho jo peeth phairay bhage chalay ja rahay hon"
  30,53,aur nah tum andhon ko un ki gumraahi se nikaal kar raah e raast dikha satke ho tum to sirf unhi ko suna satke ho jo hamari ayaat par imaan laatay aur sar-e tasleem khham kar dete hain
  30,54,"Allah hi to hai jis ne zeaf ki haalat mein tumhari paidaiesh ki ibtida ki, phir is zeaf ke baad tumhe qowat bakhsh, phir is qowat ke baad tumhe zaeef aur boorha kar diya woh jo kuch chahta hai peda karta hai aur woh sab kuch jan-nay wala, har cheez par qudrat rakhnay wala hai"
  30,55,"aur jab woh saa-at barpaa ho gi to mujrim kasmain kha kha kar kahin ge ke hum aik gharri bhar se ziyada nahi thire hain, isi terhan woh duniya ki zindagi mein dhoka khaya karte thay"
  30,56,"magar jo ilm aur imaan se behra mand kiye gay thay woh kahin ge ke khuda ke noshte mein to tum rozِ hashar taq parre rahay ho, so yeh wohi rozِ hashar hai, lekin tum jantay nah thay"
  30,57,pas woh din ho ga jis mein zaalmon ko un ki moazrat koi naffa nah day gi aur nah un se maffi mangnay ke liye kaha jaye ga
  30,58,"hum ne iss quran mein logon ko terhan terhan se samjhaya hai tum khuwa koi nishani le aao, jin logon ne maan-ne se inkaar kar diya hai woh yahi kahin ge ke tum baatil par ho"
  30,59,iss terhan thp_h laga deta hai Allah unn logon ke dilon par jo be ilm hain
  30,60,"pas ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) sabr karo, yaqeenan Allah ka wada sacha hai, aur hargiz halka nah payen tum ko woh log jo yaqeen nahi laatay"
